quran[45]{c,v,t}:
  36,60,Mbega sinaba buriye mwebwe bantu yuko muto hirahira ngo musenge Shetani mu vy’ukuri n’umwansi wanyu ari k’umugaragaro
  36,61,Yuko mwonsenga jewe Mana yanyu kuko ariyo nziza igororotse
  36,62,Ntankeka Shetani yarazimije abantu benshi cane muri mwebwe mbega ico gihe nti mwiyumvira
  36,63,Rero uwu niwo wamuriro udahera witiriwe Jahannamu mwamye mwemererwa n’Imana yanyu y’ukuri
  36,64,Uno musi uri hejuru nimu winjire mwo kubera ubuhakanyi bwanyu
  36,65,Kuri uwo musi tuzoziba iminwa yabo hanyuma amaboko yabo atuganirire ateko amaguru yabo abe ivyabona kuvyo bamye n’ivyemezo n’amaguru yabo abe kuvyo bahora bagira
  36,66,"Iyo dushaka twari kunogora amaso yabo bakaguma birukira mumayira, mugabo izo nzira bazibone gute"
  36,67,"Iyo dushaka twari kubagira ibikoko ubwo nyene naho bari, rero ntibari gushobora kugenda iyo baja canke gusubira inyuma iyo bavuye"
  36,68,"Nuwo duhaye ubuzima burebure tumusubiza inyuma mw’ishusho ryiwe ryambere, mbega ibi vyose ntibabishira mubwenge bwabo"
  36,69,"Natwe ntitwa mwigishije amajambo y’ubuhizi kandi ntivyoba kuriwe, kandi ntiyari kuba iyi Qur’aani ntagatifu atari uko ari icibutso n’igitabu kigaragaza ibikenewe vyose k’umugaragaro"
  36,70,Kugira ngo atuze uwuri muzima muribo kandi hemezwe ijambo kubatemera Imana yabo y’ukuri
  36,71,Mbega ntibabona yuko twebwe twabaremeye muvyo amaboko yacu yagize hamwe n’ibikoko batunze
  36,72,Nivyo bikoko twarabi gamburukije rero murivyo birurirwa n’ibindi navyo biraribwa
  36,73,"No muri ivyo bikoko barabironkera mwo akamaro kenshi hamwe n’ibinyobwa, mbega nikuki badashima"
  36,74,"Bagumanye\tizindi\tMana\taho\tkugumana\tImana\ty’ukuri\tkugira\tngo bafashwe nabo"
  36,75,Ntibashobora kubafasha nabo arizo ngabo zabo ziba cungereye
  36,76,"Rero ntibigutere agahinda kubera amajambo yabo, ntankeka twebwe dufise ubumenyi bw’ivyo banyegeza hamwe nivyo basemerera"
  36,77,"Mbega\tumuntu\tntazi\tyuko\ttwamuremye\tmw’Ima\try’intanga?\tnone yabaye mukeba wacu ari k’umugaragaro"
  36,78,"Yaradutangiyeko akarorero aribagira ukuremwa kwiwe aca avuga ati:- ni nde azozura amagufa y’abantu mugihe azoba yamaze kuvungagurika"
  36,79,"Vuga uti:- uwuzo yazura nurya yayaremye ubwambere, nawe n’uwufise ubumenyi bwukurema ibiremwa vyose"
  36,80,Niyo yabagiriye umukomezwa uvuye mugiti kibisi mukaba kuri ico giti namwe mucatsako
  36,81,"Mbega uwaremye Amajuru n’Isi mbega ntabushobozi afise bwukurema nk’aba yaremye, kubera iki nawe ari Umuremyi mukuru nyene ubumenyi bw’ibintu vyose"
  36,82,"Mu vy’ukuri itegeko ryiwe mugihe ishakiye ikintu icarico cose nukukibwira iti:- nube mumwanya isase kigaca kiba"
  36,83,"Aninahazwa ry’uwufise muminwe yiwe harimwo ubwami bw’ibintu vyose, niwe niho muzo subizwayo mwese"
  37,1,Ndarahiye kubatonze imirongo n’iyindi
  37,2,Kandi kuri barya batuza amabi yose
  37,3,Kandi kuri barya basoma ubutumwa bw’Imana
  37,4,Mu vy’ukuri Imana yanyu niyo yonyene gusa
  37,5,"Umuremyi\tw’Amajuru\tn’Isi\thamwe\tnibimwo\thagati\tyavyo\tkandi n’Umuremyi w’ubuseruko bwose"
  37,6,Ntankeka twebwe twarasharije Ijuru riri hafi kw’isharizo ry’Inyenyeri
  37,7,Nukuyi kingira n’amashetani yataye umurongo
  37,8,"Ntibashobore\tkwumviriza\tibiremwa\tvyeranda\tno\tmugihe\tbirukanywe kumpande zose"
  37,9,"Bazoshirwa kure, kandi bazoba bafise n’ibihano bitazoba vako"
  37,10,"Dukuye\tmwo\tuwusahuye\tikintu\tgitoyi\tmunyuma\tagaca\takurikiranwa n’igishirira gisayangana"
  37,11,"Nimubabaze muti:- mbega nibo bafise ishusho rikomeye cane canke barya twaremye, ntankeka ni twebwe twabaremye tubakuye mw’ivu rimatanye n’irindi"
  37,12,Mbega uratangara nabo babifata minenerwe
  37,13,Mugihe batujijwe ntiba gondozwa
  37,14,Mugihe babonye ibitangaro vyacu babifata minenerwe
  37,15,"Nukuvuga\tbati:-\tntivyari\tkuba\tibi\tvyose\tatari\tuko\tari\tuburozi\tburi k’umugaragaro"
  37,16,Mbega mugihe tuzosandaba nukuba ivu n’amagufa niko kuzoba ari ukuri kukuzurwa
  37,17,N’abatama bacu bakera
  37,18,"Vuga uti:- egome muri ico gihe muzoba muri mubihano bitazoba vako"
  37,19,Iyo mumuriro udahera hazoba hari induru yurutavana ko munyuma yaho bazobona umuhero w’Isi washitse
  37,20,"Bazovuga bati:- yo! Uwu niwo wamusi w’impembo"
  37,21,Uwu niwo musi wugucibwa urubanza mwahora muhakana